### **3. 23_LogStreamFocus**  
**Description:**  
Filters and groups log entries based on frequency, timestamps, and keywords.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LogStreamFocus - Log Filtering & Grouping Tool

LogStreamFocus is designed to help you detect frequent log patterns, error surges, and anomalies in real-time or static logs.

## Features
- Repetition grouping  
- Keyword trigger alerts  
- Lightweight and fast  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/23_LogStreamFocus.git
cd 23_LogStreamFocus
python analyze.py logs/system.log
